Module java.desktop
Package javax.swing.text.html.parser

Class TagElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.text.html.parser.TagElement
  • public class TagElement
extends Object
    A generic HTML TagElement class. The methods define how white space is interpreted around the tag.
